Indonesian Energy Minister Subroto said OPEC deliberately production ceiling 15.8 mln barrel defend 18 dlr barrel price target .
He told reporter energy conference Jakarta OPEC decided maintain price level 18 dlrs .
`` We deliberately defending price , OPEC production le 15.8 ( mln ) moment , '' stated .
Asked OPEC would increase production price went 18 dlrs barrel , said would decided next OPEC meeting June .
`` We discus market situation , '' added .
He said meeting OPEC Differentials Committee postponed `` need meeting .
'' He elaborate .
The committee originally due meet Vienna week .
